# usr/

User-facing documentation for Intent v2.4.0. Contains three comprehensive guides covering installation, task-oriented workflows, and system reference. These documents are the primary resources for users learning and using Intent.

## Files

- `user_guide.md` -- Task-oriented guide for common Intent workflows: steel threads, backlog, documentation, LLM collaboration, treeindex, skills, and subagent management
- `reference_guide.md` -- Comprehensive reference covering all commands, document templates, directory structure, configuration options, and best practices
- `deployment_guide.md` -- Deployment instructions for various environments: installation methods, configuration, integration, maintenance, upgrading, and troubleshooting
